 \sum_{k=n+1}^{\infty}\frac{1}{k!}  =\frac{1}{(n+1)!}+ \sum_{k=n+2}^{\infty}\frac{1}{k!} \leq \frac{1}{(n+1)!}+ \sum_{k=n+2}^{\infty}\frac{1}{n!(k-1)k}
= \frac{1}{(n+1)!}+\frac{1}{n!}\sum_{k=n+2}^{\infty}\frac{1}{(k-1)k} =\frac{1}{(n+1)!}+\frac{1}{n!}\frac{1}{n+1}
\sum_{k=n+2}^{\infty}\frac{1}{(k-1)k}=\frac{1}{(n+2)-1}
